# Zephyria Wallet Extension — Build Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A complete, production-ready Firefox browser wallet extension for the Zephyria blockchain.

**Location:** `/Users/karan/sol2zig/wallet-extension/`  
**Load from:** `/Users/karan/sol2zig/wallet-extension/dist/`

